553
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:34,080
[Suk-bong] Stand up straight, fuckers.

554
00:30:35,250 --> 00:30:36,910
Those who joined in December.

555
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:39,170
Private Kang Byeong-su, sir!

556
00:30:39,250 --> 00:30:40,750
Private Shin Gwang-seop, sir!

557
00:30:40,830 --> 00:30:42,340
Private Jeon Eun-seok, sir!

558
00:30:43,090 --> 00:30:44,420
