572
00:31:18,290 --> 00:31:20,670
-Private Shin Gwang-seop, sir!
-Private Jeon Eun-seok, sir!

573
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:22,880
Get up.

574
00:31:25,710 --> 00:31:26,750
[sand rumbles]

575
00:31:28,010 --> 00:31:29,510
