576
00:31:31,340 --> 00:31:32,970
Hyeon-min and Jeong-in.

577
00:31:33,930 --> 00:31:34,800
You should do better.

578
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:37,220
[Hyeon-min and Jeong-in] Yes, sir.

579
00:31:37,310 --> 00:31:40,230
