just want the best for you guys.

580
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:41,440
Go back inside.

581
00:31:50,190 --> 00:31:51,280
What are you doing?

582
00:31:51,910 --> 00:31:52,820
[Jun-ho] I'm sorry, sir.

583
00:31:53,820 --> 00:31:55,580
But we also got beaten up a lot.

584
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,410
So let's stop this…

585
00:31:57,490 --> 00:32:01,920
You didn't even get beat up that much!
You were never here since you're a D.P.

586
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:04,380
[Sung-bok breathes heavily]

587
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:06,710
I'm sorry, sir.

588
00:32:07,590 --> 00:32:08,920
But still…

589
00:32:09,010 --> 00:32:10,010
[soldier grunts]

590
00:32:10,090 --> 00:32:12,430
Private Kang Byeong-su, sir.

591
00:32:13,130 --> 00:32:16,510
Gosh, I'm getting discharged soon,
so I wasn't going to get involved.

592
00:32:18,810 --> 00:32:21,640
-Front leaning rest position, Nerd.
-Private Cho Suk-bong, sir.

593
00:32:23,390 --> 00:32:24,850
[Jang-soo] You asshole…

594
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:28,230
Should you be so strict
to someone fresh out of the boot?

595
00:32:28,320 --> 00:32:29,360
No, sir.

596
00:32:30,780 --> 00:32:34,280
-Sergeant Hwang, please stop--
